trans-unit.source: Defines a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en samling av <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> representing the number of elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>som representerer antall elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of elements by their name.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av elementer med navnet.

trans-unit.source: While the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A> property of an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement> must be unique, multiple elements can use the same <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Mens den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A>for en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement>må være unik, flere elementer kan bruke samme <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name or ID of the element.
trans-unit.target: Navnet eller IDen for elementet.

trans-unit.source: An containing the elements whose property match name.
trans-unit.target: En som inneholder elementer som egenskapen samsvarer name .

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en opplisting som går gjennom en samling.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets an item from the collection by specifying its numerical index.
trans-unit.target: Henter en elementet fra samlingen ved å angi den numeriske indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Elements in an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection> are not guaranteed to be in source code order.
trans-unit.target: Elementer i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection>ikke garanteres i kilden kode order.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: In other words, just because a `DIV` element is the first element inside of a `BODY` tag does not mean that the first element of the collection will be the `DIV` element.
trans-unit.target: Utelukkende med andre ord, fordi en `DIV` elementet er det første elementet i for en `BODY` koden ikke betyr at det første elementet i samlingen blir den `DIV` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The position from which to retrieve an item from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Posisjonen som ikke hente et element fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An item from the collection by specifying its numerical index.
trans-unit.target: Et element fra samlingen ved å angi den numeriske indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Gets an item from the collection by specifying its name.
trans-unit.target: Henter en elementet fra samlingen ved å angi navnet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name*> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id*> attribute of the element.
trans-unit.target: Den <> </> *> eller <> </> *>-attributtet for elementet.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"></xref>, if the named element is found.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"> </xref>, hvis elementet navngitt finnes.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the collection to an <xref:System.Array>, starting at a particular <xref:System.Array> index.
trans-unit.target: Overfører av elementene i samlingen til en <xref:System.Array>, med Start fra en bestemt <xref:System.Array>indeksen.</xref:System.Array> </xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from collection.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>som er målet for elementene kopieres fra samlingen.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` som kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om tilgang til den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection"> </xref> er synkronisert (tråden trygt).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> in all cases.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>i alle tilfeller.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>
